{"tid":832591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「搏命」外傭危站高層伸逾半身抹外窗 網民呼牙煙","createTime":"2018-09-23T01:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T08:24:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"25bc2a6e6d50a25465665a53fcced11a384976a9","tid":832591,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mKRDSIvbyvNGwR28csDlXQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/485c8bce109595eaf14891dfc1d17f15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmKRDSIvbyvNGwR28csDlXQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F485c8bce109595eaf14891dfc1d17f15&h=19eb8746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日（22日）社交網站Facebook瘋傳一張相片，相中一名「搏命」的外傭姐姐，在大廈高層一個單位，站於外牆不足3吋闊石壆，幾乎大半個身都在窗外，右手抓緊屋內窗框，左手用布抹拭外窗，惟看不到她有用安全帶，亦不見有人協助扶穩，情況險象環生。<br />\n<br />\n有網民看見相片後，擔心她稍一失足便飛落街，寫上「This is wrong . Totally wrong」(這是錯，全錯)等字眼，相片上載10個小時，已有多達1萬1千個分享、及超過2千人熱烈討論，惟實際發生的地點及時間還未清楚。<br />\n<br />\n勞工處早前與外傭的輸出國家訂明抹外窗的條款，2017年1月1日生效，新條例列明僱主須在走廊、地面或平台以外的窗戶，加設上鎖或固定窗花，否則不可要求外傭進行抹窗工作；外傭手臂以外的身體部分不得伸出窗外。"},{"pid":"665b96ea70a62ddb27a3a65ba0c07dbc1801f6b4","tid":832591,"uid":159851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"煙屎牙"},{"pid":"6079c341e2dddc661634f5acbb3776c3b078e813","tid":832591,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:36:05.000Z","msg":"她一直在玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439522295b35dce3bacae6f1cae683164570b49d","tid":832591,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ef30459f866971c7c41e1563d047a9cf1d57bca","tid":832591,"uid":12554,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23